  <entry>
    <title>Markdown用法</title>
    <link href="/2023/01/31/Markdown%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <url>/2023/01/31/Markdown%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>下面介绍常用的Markdown语法</p><h1 id="一号标题"><a href="#一号标题" class="headerlink" title="一号标题"></a>一号标题</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二号标题"><a href="#二号标题" class="headerlink" title="二号标题"></a>二号标题</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三号标题"><a href="#三号标题" class="headerlink" title="三号标题"></a>三号标题</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="四号标题"><a href="#四号标题" class="headerlink" title="四号标题"></a>四号标题</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="五号标题"><a href="#五号标题" class="headerlink" title="五号标题"></a>五号标题</h5><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="六号标题"><a href="#六号标题" class="headerlink" title="六号标题"></a>六号标题</h6><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>文字加粗</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**文字加粗**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>文字倾斜</em></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*文字倾斜*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>文字加粗倾斜</strong></em></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*文字加粗倾斜*</span>**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><del>文字删除线效果</del></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~文字删除线效果~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">分割线：--- 或 <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://llyth.cn/img/favicon.ico" alt="图片效果示例" title="图片效果示例"></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">插入图片：![<span class="string">图片alt</span>](<span class="link">图片地址 &quot;图片title&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://llyth.cn/" title="超链接示例">超链接示例</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">插入链接：[<span class="string">超链接名</span>](<span class="link">超链接地址 &quot;超链接title&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>无序列表</li><li>无序列表</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">无序列表：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 无序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 无序列表</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 无序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 无序列表</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 无序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：符号和内容之间有一个空格（这和加粗倾斜不同，加粗倾斜符号和文本之间没有空格）</p><ol><li>有序列表</li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">有序列表：1. 有序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>表头</th><th>表头</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>单元格</td><td>单元格</td></tr><tr><td>单元格</td><td>单元格</td></tr><tr><td>单元格</td><td>单元格</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">表格：</span><br><span class="line">|  表头   | 表头  |</span><br><span class="line">|  ----  | ----  |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格  | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格  | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格  | 单元格 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>表格文字默认左对齐，如果需要调整对齐格式，需要在分隔表头和其他行的不同位置添加<code>:</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 左对齐 | 右对齐 | 居中对齐 |</span><br><span class="line">| :-----| ----: | :----: |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格 | 单元格 | 单元格 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th align="center">居中对齐</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Hexo默认主题可能不支持表格修改对齐方式</p><p><code>行间代码</code></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`行间代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">代码块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```代码语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">代码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Hexo默认主题不支持显示代码语种</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
